title: District President Logo
content: Blue Color Represents Lions whom that are the Guiding Light and the Pillars of Strength of the LEO movement. Green Color Sustainability in Leadership focus and healthy growth in Membership.    Gold Color Sustainability focus to Lead, in the ever-changing macro environment.    Four Human figures gathered with a hand held high Intent to achieve the four key focus areas of the program; Sustainable Skills Sustainable Knowledge Sustainable Projects Sustainable Social Behavioral Lifestyle
